<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/faq.css">
  <title>FAQ - AgroTech SL</title>
  <style>
    .faq-toggle .fa-times {
      display: none;
    }

    .faq.active .fa-chevron-down {
      display: none;
    }

    .faq.active .fa-times {
      display: inline;
    }

    .red {
      color: red;
      margin: 0 0.5rem;
    }

    .faq {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .faq-title {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .faq-text {
      display: none;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .faq.active .faq-text {
      display: block;
    }

    .faq-toggle {
      background: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Frequently Asked Questions - AgroTech SL</h1>
  <div class="faq-container">
    <div class="faq active">
      <h3 class="faq-title">
        What services does AgroTech SL offer?
      </h3>
      <p class="faq-text">
        AgroTech SL provides a platform for Sierra Leonean farmers to access resources, expert advice, market prices, and a network of other farmers. We offer support in improving crop yields, sustainable farming practices, and using technology in agriculture.
      </p>
      <button class="faq-toggle">
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
        <i class="fas fa-times red"></i>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3 class="faq-title">
        How can AgroTech SL help increase my farm's productivity?
      </h3>
      <p class="faq-text">
        Through our platform, we provide tailored farming tips, crop management advice, and updates on modern agricultural techniques. We also offer guidance on using fertilizers, pest control, and soil management to help you maximize your yields sustainably.
      </p>
      <button class="faq-toggle">
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
        <i class="fas fa-times red"></i>
      </button>
    </div>
    
    <div class="faq">
      <h3 class="faq-title">
        Does AgroTech SL provide information on crop pricing?
      </h3>
      <p class="faq-text">
        Yes, AgroTech SL provides current market prices for various crops. This information helps farmers make informed decisions about when to sell their produce and understand market trends.
      </p>
      <button class="faq-toggle">
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
        <i class="fas fa-times red"></i>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3 class="faq-title">
        What crops are best suited for Sierra Leone’s climate?
      </h3>
      <p class="faq-text">
        Sierra Leone’s climate supports crops such as rice, cassava, maize, and groundnuts. Our platform offers resources on the ideal planting and harvesting times, as well as crop rotation practices to ensure soil fertility.
      </p>
      <button class="faq-toggle">
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
        <i class="fas fa-times red"></i>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3 class="faq-title">
        How does AgroTech SL support sustainable farming practices?
      </h3>
      <p class="faq-text">
        We emphasize the importance of sustainable practices like crop rotation, organic fertilization, and soil conservation. Through our resources, we guide farmers on eco-friendly techniques that preserve soil health and improve productivity in the long term.
      </p>
      <button class="faq-toggle">
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
        <i class="fas fa-times red"></i>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3 class="faq-title">
        Can I get expert advice on pest and disease management?
      </h3>
      <p class="faq-text">
        Absolutely. AgroTech SL offers resources and connects you with agricultural experts who can provide advice on pest and disease control to help protect your crops.
      </p>
      <button class="faq-toggle">
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
        <i class="fas fa-times red"></i>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3 class="faq-title">
        How can I join AgroTech SL and start using its services?
      </h3>
      <p class="faq-text">
        You can register through our platform by creating an account. Once registered, you’ll have access to all of our farming tips, resources, and community support.
      </p>
      <button class="faq-toggle">
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
        <i class="fas fa-times red"></i>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/js/all.min.js"></script>
  <script>
    const toggles = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-toggle');

    toggles.forEach(toggle => {
      toggle.addEventListener('click', () => {
        toggle.parentNode.classList.toggle('active');
      });
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
